    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/f4cb8c1a721e37e0d2687dee4b4ec942.poster.avif?t=1677495535\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/f4cb8c1a721e37e0d2687dee4b4ec942.webm?t=1677495535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/f4cb8c1a721e37e0d2687dee4b4ec942.mp4?t=1677495535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏玩法：<br>只需要在敌人接近你的防守区域之前发射技能消灭他就可以取得胜利。<br>每个敌人都有不同的伤害数量，你可以通过获取能量宝石来生成同伴，合成同伴可以增加攻击数量，还可以使用高级技能对敌人造成加倍的伤害，最终消灭所有敌人之后就可以取得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/6c0ef2e1f9c175384fe919f6a04f84d2.avif?t=1677495535\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras_big/6c0ef2e1f9c175384fe919f6a04f84d2.avif?t=1677495535 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>游戏特色：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/92c77bcc4b29c15ff3eef0542aeb1895.avif?t=1677495535\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras_big/92c77bcc4b29c15ff3eef0542aeb1895.avif?t=1677495535 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>1、闯关解锁：<br>游戏有4关，难度逐渐增加，闯关之后可以解锁下一关，每一关的BOSS都有隐藏的伤害技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/1874d0d304f890ef5eed6c312120da54.avif?t=1677495535\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras_big/1874d0d304f890ef5eed6c312120da54.avif?t=1677495535 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>2、选择英雄：<br>你有3个英雄可以选择，每个英雄都有一个高级技能，使用高级技能可以给敌人造成加倍的伤害。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras/ffa91a972e756f7e604a88946c1c283f.avif?t=1677495535\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220710/extras_big/ffa91a972e756f7e604a88946c1c283f.avif?t=1677495535 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>3、合成英雄：<br>获取能量宝石后可以生成同伴，合成同伴可以增加攻击数量，和同伴一起防守家园，消灭来犯之敌。",
